{"tid":2132680,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"西營盤社區綜合大樓出現確診個案 社區會堂要消毒","createTime":"2020-07-30T13:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T16:00:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5c94b0555273a9d7c63fdc3187c77fdcff7cfdca","tid":2132680,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:42:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/124942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F124942&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSgy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=d1debb65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/124942</a><br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署表示，西營盤社區綜合大樓出現新型肺炎確診個案，大樓內的社區會堂今晚將進行全面消毒及清潔，大樓今日曾開放給市民食用自攜午膳。中西區的夜間臨時避暑中心今晚將改設於堅尼地城社區綜合大樓一樓，直至另行通告，明日開放給市民食用自攜午膳的地點，會改為堅尼地城社區綜合大樓二樓。<br />\n<br />\n2020-07-30 21:34:09"},{"pid":"2b48c90e024f0a0b490292bbc364c4a4e905d234","tid":2132680,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:43:43.000Z","msg":"攬炒"},{"pid":"f5b2ed6974c1b50a9d91d9e01f4072636f612c12","tid":2132680,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d266d86445704cca5aac79a528a7168727ad4f00","tid":2132680,"uid":195167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:44:55.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7de7234195091b6554f573501f096c495d014f","tid":2132680,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:45:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkg